title: [FEATURE] Add the ability to set offsets to an overlay hole (issue #6). Offset…
message: [FEATURE] Add the ability to set offsets to an overlay hole (issue #6). Offset values (left and top, both can be either positive or negative integers, in pixels) are stored in a two-value array in a field of the Overlay class. Overlay.setHoleOffsets() is provided for setting those values to an overlay instance.
